{"tid":1942183,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急告急］蘇豪黃酒吧 咲の木 賣日本生啤唔擺得耐 現買一送一但求不浪費","createTime":"2020-03-25T02:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T03:50:29.000Z","uid":48083,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9572d9998370a6024c48162c4c01ed2b4b3132","tid":1942183,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7jKjkZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7jKjkZ.png&h=7c2ab021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前一個月蝕緊6位數都撐醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qv2zGzm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqv2zGzm.png&h=f3c80fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3VJzUn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3VJzUn.png&h=fc8f2073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年一月在蘇豪開業，主打日本手工啤酒的酒吧咲の木，剛開業就遇上世紀疫情，老闆Esther坦承﹕「輸少當贏，希望每個月可以收支平衡，起碼（虧損）六位數回落到五位數，我想已經很開心。」她表示一月中剛開業時，生意額一直穩步上揚，但是疫情傳出後，「2月1日開始跌，跌到谷底，中環始終是遊客區，香港遊客由數十萬跌到每日只有三千。」<br />\n<br />\n為了自救，咲の木擴展消夜時段，「原來這區深夜沒有熟食，所以我們營業到凌晨5時，不少人喝酒後，需要吃飯時便會過來。」所以亦有不少食客上門，Jason﹕「以前一星期會來三四次，現在就只來一次，我會維持最低限度，出去走一走。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=3_60678975&amp;i=20200307\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D3_60678975%26i%3D20200307&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=9063aa9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D3_60678975%26i%3D20200307&h=132f5a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=3_60678975&amp;i=20200307</a>"},{"pid":"16acc85e4326e938e14bf6a988bb98509c83